sub_title: Trainee at the Royal Norwegian Embassy in The Hague  |  Advanced MSc International Relations and Diplomacy
summary:
With a solid foundation in political, economic, and security studies, I continuously seek opportunities to expand my knowledge, develop skills, and create a positive impact.

I am currently a trainee at the Royal Norwegian Embassy in The Hague working on the bilateral relations between Norway and the Netherlands/Luxembourg. I am also a nominated candidate for the Nordre Follo Municipal Elections in Norway and serve as a board member for the European Movement Follo. I am also currently pursuing an Advanced MSc in International Relations and Diplomacy at Leiden University
